      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干搭起来。main分支在ONE之后继续TWO提交，然后从develop cherry-pick A过来，再做一个THREE提交。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit TWO",
