    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，main分支还需要从featureA cherry-pick那个FIX提交，这样才算\"from each\"。然后develop分支最后要merge featureA。",
